Next Steps:
===========

After deployment to Vercel:
1. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel project dashboard
2. Navigate to the Analytics section and click "Enable"
3. Verify tracking by checking browser Network tab for requests to `/_vercel/insights/view`
4. View analytics data in the Vercel dashboard

Notes:
======

- The Analytics component is lightweight and doesn't require any additional configuration
